{"tid":1745964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"清潔工今日下午旺角洗衣街 搵到50汽油彈","createTime":"2019-11-22T13:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T13:41:07.000Z","uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98aac37f5035b8d90d8b1b50b138e314cb84409f","tid":1745964,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"旺角洗衣街一條後巷發現大量汽油彈，警方到場調查，多名防暴警員到場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n現場是洗衣街239號旁邊一條橫巷，警方下午約3時接獲市民報案，指上址發現一批汽油彈。警員到場，將現場圍封調查。據悉，經點算後，初步證實有4箱汽油彈，每箱有10多枚，警方在場另檢獲多個空樽及仍未入樽的汽油。<br />\n<br />\n涉案現場對面是界限街1號體育館，周日將作為區議會選舉投票站，警方正追查該批汽油彈的來源及使用動機。多名防暴警員到場戒備，警方到鄰近停車場取走閉路電視錄影，案件交旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進案件。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有街坊早前曾看見有私家車及客貨車停泊，有人分批將汽油彈載至上址。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1143854/即時-香港-旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈-警查來源動機\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1143854%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E8%BF%9150%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=8a29da56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1143854%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E8%BF%9150%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F&h=c762d547\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1143854/即時-香港-旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈-警查來源動機</a>"},{"pid":"836d132febdda4695ff87f92a82f60be3cbb5cee","tid":1745964,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"小心行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc4fefbe53ab6815641ae9b044f77d75337fbe","tid":174